Name: Winnie The Pooh: The Serial Killer
About the game: Winnie The Pooh: The Serial Killer is a third person shooter were your goal is to get the best score. Winnie The Pooh can kill civilians and enemies by ranged weapons. Winnie The Pooh can use a hostile approach by using ranged weapons to kill as many enemies as possible. The game has many enemy types including melee police, pistol police, sniper police and even helicopters. This game has many wanted levels which will affect the spawned police.
